Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
