Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
